        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .visit-button {\n    display: inline-block;\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    padding: 12px 28px;\n    background-color: #111;\n    color: #fff;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .visit-button:hover {\n    background-color: #333;\n  }\n  .warranty-detail {\n    background: #f9f9f9;\n    padding: 60px 20px;\n  }\n  .detail-block {\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto 60px auto;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .detail-block h3 {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .detail-block p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n  .detail-icon {\n    width: 64px;\n    height: 64px;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"warranty-detail\">\n  <div class=\"detail-block\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/8031/8031372.png\" alt=\"2-Year Warranty Icon\" class=\"detail-icon\">\n    <h3>2 Years Coverage</h3>\n    <p>Every repair we complete includes a 2-year warranty. This applies to screens, batteries, logic boards, and all other services. We stand by the durability of our work.</p>\n    <p>The warranty applies whether you visit us in London or send your device from anywhere in the country.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"detail-block\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2910/2910768.png\" alt=\"Built to Last Icon\" class=\"detail-icon\">\n    <h3>Built to Last</h3>\n    <p>We use original Apple parts wherever possible, sourced and tested to meet factory standards. Combined with precision workmanship from experienced engineers, our repairs are made to last.</p>\n    <p>Every device goes through our full testing process before it leaves. We check what we fixed and everything else. Problems get caught before you see them.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"detail-block\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/7920/7920222.png\" alt=\"Logic Board Icon\" class=\"detail-icon\">\n    <h3>Logic Board Repairs Covered</h3>\n    <p>Logic board repairs are included in the 2-year warranty. We do not handle complex repairs differently. If something fails, we fix it.</p>\n    <p>This level of confidence applies to every repair we take on.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"detail-block\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/10240/10240281.png\" alt=\"Evidence Based Icon\" class=\"detail-icon\">\n    <h3>Transparent, Evidence Based Decisions</h3>\n    <p>If a repaired device fails, we inspect it properly and show you the findings. We explain clearly why it failed, whether it is covered, and we support this with photos and proof.</p>\n    <p>There is no fine print. You get direct answers and full clarity every time.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"detail-block\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/6146/6146665.png\" alt=\"Easy Claim Icon\" class=\"detail-icon\">\n    <h3>Simple and Fair Claims</h3>\n    <p>If you need to use the warranty, contact us or submit a claim using the form below. We will inspect your device and handle it if the issue is covered.</p>\n    <p>Our process is designed to help you and avoid unnecessary complications.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
